  "title": "이번에는 직원들끼리만 회식 [이수한의원 남성역한의원 사당동한의원]",
  "addDate": "2018. 2. 20.",
  "categoryNo": "43",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=221212505414",
  "html_size": 196187,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view221212505414\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea221212505414\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p>안녕하세요~</p><p><br /></p><p>저희 이수한의원 직원들이 처음으로 원장님 없이 회식을 했네요..</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>사실</p><p>2개월동안 함께 한 알바샘이 이제 그만 둬요 ㅠㅠ</p><p><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e99805d963476e94.png\" alt=\"moon_and_james-12\"></a>&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>원래 2개월만 하기로 한거라... 잡을수가없네요&nbsp;</p><p>알바샘의 꿈을 위해 멀리 외국으로 가신데요 ㅠㅠ</p><p><br /></p><p>잡고싶다</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>그래서 직원들끼리 모여서 같이 식사를 했습니다</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>아! 우리 이수한의원 원장님께서 회식비용은 지원해주셨습니다</p><p><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/line_characters_in_love\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/00480f2a1a576e9d.png\" alt=\"line_characters_in_love-7\"></a>&nbsp;</p><p>감사합니다! #꾸벅</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>이수역에 있는 서가앤쿡으로 갔어요</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5587cd27e93dddbf.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 550px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMjBfMjQw/MDAxNTE5MTA5MjgzOTQw.DjCUjaFTfxH82atO60XCt39Miv8j0c4HYXnYv2pqe10g.KEtXMclEkb1SFz9MxeJs9G8USNNHcus-UcyDISngbC4g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180220_103939570.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033814AF546')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5587cd27e93dddbf.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5d77e3cd818649b0.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 550px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMjBfNzAg/MDAxNTE5MTA5Mjg0NTUw.4DnPF0hK3pV29g_Xkli6Ll7_Sd1aYvzAdrCtk61tzWIg.wary_rUlPJg9rRIvmFzRmu1hP36yh0QmJ6EDiXVC29gg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180220_103939760.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033814AF546')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5d77e3cd818649b0.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>서가앤쿡 한상차림 두개와 고르곤졸라 피자 한개 주문했어요</p><p><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9d43f4253686d08a.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 550px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMjBfMjU2/MDAxNTE5MTA5Mjg0Njg2.2mv_JZ5KM0VoJb2Fc1RVpd5xTCv5WcZamBHMSaDZQZ4g.A-b0vUkDtJf1caytnlNSddGtJkU6SUprziaf8TuXyMkg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180220_103940532.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033814AF546')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9d43f4253686d08a.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>해산물 토마스 파스타 + 게살 오이스터 리조또<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/404eb6c20b504308.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 550px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMjBfMjU1/MDAxNTE5MTA5Mjg0ODI2.ceeaKh8M0r6I0GhjxR9wjwR4OSiZv5XkY2Kt6EQ7t2cg.D_TjQlVKBru5EpYW_r0Y6cZUwgV-WpILp04KROsQXFgg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180220_103940051.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033814AF546')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/404eb6c20b504308.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9fe6be466a48b22b.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 550px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMjBfMTIy/MDAxNTE5MTA5Mjg1MDA1.mKoBGEJ1_0hGLj7d259Z6KXlWYuT3mEHedRpsFH6Foog.OoRRC-WAardud5NMUz-5PaZsJu1xGHSjPdUSM2rXYIcg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180220_103940292.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033814AF546')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9fe6be466a48b22b.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/308ac5522e791aaa.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 550px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMjBfOTMg/MDAxNTE5MTA5Mjg1MTgz.nbzzn-fy7-tqoNATRKTD3fZdsNklkT0m4FPhjOQCOZUg.W5r9bYunh_Aja-gyjyfnVpEPehncmKALCESmRh2JPVAg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180220_103941042.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033814AF546')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/308ac5522e791aaa.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>목살 스테이크 샐러드&nbsp;+ 베이컨 까르보나라<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a62fce2bbea1f5a9.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 550px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMjBfMTgx/MDAxNTE5MTA5Mjg1MjY1.XjHM-aY-1Se6aW4xmLsf0EfSPXI5wJmQU6TvcbxdD4Yg.9nhyD0C4XtPvXJdNPl6Tm2XuHj6EF9X9lExtDRqUIMEg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180220_103940737.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033814AF546')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a62fce2bbea1f5a9.jpg\"></p><p><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/639dee3d1ea895b4.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 550px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMjBfODQg/MDAxNTE5MTA5Mjg1NDI2.I48waPkCKAPY2SBjrXsvP4XlUZ2HEDn7F11xtosIfwQg.2UMuwN_F9rfYzPbzUn24nWFPDGNnF88ANlezqky4PDIg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180220_103940894.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033814AF546')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/639dee3d1ea895b4.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/61597a3347439edb.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 550px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMjBfNDQg/MDAxNTE5MTA5Mjg1NjU3.diwDFS9mXE0CkNE6dBsuAiyNSed1VU_eQqCQqIJwFN8g.dXGAOTxn0GQ-zEwDd82oJJUxORO6-pMm13d1WG8Umksg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180220_103941185.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033814AF546')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/61597a3347439edb.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>고로곤졸라 피자 with Honey<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/683889f46f7cb4c0.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 550px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMjBfMTAw/MDAxNTE5MTA5Mjg1ODA0.fXPZ35T67TQAX8vscZpKamm9XZn0PpoLbld7y1FZmXIg.0WzUmHzIUL53C60Ha3T_xFt_KtHPHcaJDEGj3LF-Zhwg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180220_103941340.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033814AF546')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/683889f46f7cb4c0.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>맛있겠죠?&nbsp;</p><p>너무 많아서 배 터질뻔...</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>다들 하나도 안남기고 깨끗히 다 먹었어요</p><p><br /></p><p>저녁시간이라 그런지</p><p>다들 배가 많이 고팠나봐요 ㅋㅋ<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/39043f4a34cae04f.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"309\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 309px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMjBfNDUg/MDAxNTE5MTA5Mjg2MDcx.CjkSmpPWeBnldXjxhtYjTvMEzYt4PhrIe4vhhtjxHbMg.y2ic-XBK8QWNGU2rO2DKT7MhoN3OaChboIaUZIiv75gg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180220_103941610.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033814AF546')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/39043f4a34cae04f.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>기념으로 사진도 찰칵!&nbsp;<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c397a6eccde639a9.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"733\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 733px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMjBfMTc3/MDAxNTE5MTA5Mjg2MTk1.qkXwKzCtyu1DYDWG81mhtSNHuUkwQIKZcZR28OAodgkg.snn4tgPth69r6hoA5uzi-dgfJ_50XrOWIT4FBkMwvXIg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180220_141959518.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033814AF546')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c397a6eccde639a9.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>더 찍으려고 했는데..</p><p>다들 부끄러워해서</p><p><br /></p><p>그냥 다 가리고 찍는걸로 컨셉을 ㅋㅋㅋ</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>맛있게 먹고</p><p>2차는 후식으로 설빙갔어요</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>뭐 먹을까 고민 하다가</p><p>딸기트리빙수로 정했어요&nbsp;</p><p><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/148e812be44bc989.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 550px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMjBfNSAg/MDAxNTE5MTA5Mjg2NDM3._-b9bUf52J-9U6otjATEo-5M2Wj4w6JxK8_mGLI0pJ8g.7Vs6IgLNeD7GPb9mxoY9TLjrZ4CWjcFP88NB8pZnsjUg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180220_103943203.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033814AF546')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/148e812be44bc989.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/dadf6d97e0110d53.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 550px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"MjAxODAyMjBfMTgx/MDAxNTE5MTA5Mjg2NzE1.pDbjumzpBt62SIwqaCaDdSJ5LE5xnFQAKhWJXNWDjMgg.IWmpWHTWkrKUkZMHl4QqrixLk9OHIsV-YHWHH_3wcyog.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20180220_103943052.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033814AF546')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/dadf6d97e0110d53.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>딸기가 상큼하고.. 맛도 깔끔하고</p><p>녹차 아이스크림도 녹차맛이 진해서 너무 맛있었어요</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>알바샘 덕분에 이렇게 직원들끼리 모여서 식사도 하고</p><p>우리 원장님 너무 감사합니다!!!</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/line_characters_in_love\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/94688b3cbf3089df.png\" alt=\"line_characters_in_love-1\"></a><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/line_characters_in_love\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/636299638ed45fe1.png\" alt=\"line_characters_in_love-4\"></a><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/line_characters_in_love\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fa78c6dc40535c86.png\" alt=\"line_characters_in_love-15\"></a>&nbsp;</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
